    dc:description "Fig. 18. Morphological features of Rhyacobates elongatus sp. nov. A. Body of female, dorsal view. B. Body of female, excluding head and prothorax, ventral view. C. Body of female, lateral view. D. Abdominal end of female, dorsal view. E. Abdominal end of female, ventral view. F. Abdominal end of female, lateral view. G. Body of male, dorsal view. H. Body of male, excluding head and prothorax, ventral view. I. Basal part of right middle leg of male, ventral view. J. Proctiger of male, dorsal view. K. Left paramere, lateral aspect, two different views. Scale bars: A–I = 1 mm; J–K = 0.2 mm." ;
